## 6. Quick reference

| Service | Datastore | Migration tool | Replication (production) | Primary-only reads required for |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| identity-service | PostgreSQL (`identity` db) | Flyway | Primary + async standby | Login, `GetUser` (auth-gating reads) |
| catalog-service | MongoDB (`catalog` db) | Flamingock | Replica set (1 primary + 2 secondaries) | `ReserveStock`, `ReleaseStock`, stock-authoritative reads |
| order-service | PostgreSQL (`orders` db) | Flyway | Primary + standby (sync standby recommended, unconfirmed RPO) | All writes; order history reads may use a replica |
| notification-service | MongoDB (`notifications` db) | Flamingock | Replica set (1 primary + 2 secondaries) | None — all reads may use `secondaryPreferred` |

